item.turbo:content:
<! [CDATA[
Evernote Logo
Evernote is an app designed for note taking, organizing, task management, and archiving. It is developed by the Evernote Corporation, headquartered in Redwood City, California. The app allows users to create notes, which can be text, drawings, photographs, audio, or saved web content. Notes are stored in notebooks and can be tagged, annotated, edited, searched, given attachments, and exported. Evernote is cross-platform, with a web client as well as applications on Android, iOS, macOS, and Microsoft Windows.
You can download theEvernotelogo on full-version of the page.
